17021","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"しみじみと、平塚静はいつかの昔を懐かしむ。","name_cn":"感慨万千、平塚静回忆往昔。","duration":"00:24:05","airdate":"2020-08-06","comment":39,"desc":"脚本：大知慶一郎 / 絵コンテ：清水 聡 / 演出：戸澤俊太郎 / 作画監督：アルベルト・キエ 安本 学 平田賢一 岡本健一郎\r\n\r\n結衣と別れ平塚の元に向かった八幡は\r\n学校側もプロム自粛の方向になっていると聞き戸惑う。\r\n「君はこれから、彼女とどう関わるつもりだ？」\r\n平塚からの質問に意を決した八幡。\r\nその向う先は生徒会室だった。八幡が提案したこととは？","status":"Air"},{"id":917022,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/917022","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"あらためて、比企谷八幡はかたりかける。","name_cn":"再一次、比企谷八幡开口述说。","duration":"00:24:05","airdate":"2020-08-13","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":917023,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/917023","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"最後まで、由比ヶ浜結衣は見守り続ける。","name_cn":"","duration":"00:24:05","airdate":"2020-08-20","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":917024,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/917024","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"せめて、もうまちがえたくないと願いながら。","name_cn":"","duration":"00:24:05","airdate":"2020-08-27","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":917025,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/917025","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"きっと、その香りをかぐたびに、思い出す季節がある。","name_cn":"","duration":"00:24:05","airdate":"2020-09-03","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":917026,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/917026","type":0,"sort":10,"name":"颯爽、平塚静は前を歩く。","name_cn":"","duration":"00:24:05","airdate":"2020-09-10","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":917027,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/917027","type":0,"sort":11,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"00:24:05","airdate":"2020-09-17","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":917028,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/917028","type":0,"sort":12,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2020-09-24","comment":1,"desc":"","status":"NA"}],"crt":[{"id":19039,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/71/60/19039_crt_BcOgO.jpg","name":"比企谷八幡","desc":"江口拓也"},{"id":19040,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/7a/02/19040_crt_wQQO2.jpg","name":"雪之下雪乃","desc":"早見沙織"},{"id":19041,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/f3/90/19041_crt_FG0PO.jpg","name":"由比滨结衣","desc":"東山奈央"},{"id":26090,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/8